</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 运行时切换策略</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">PaymentStrategy</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">strategy</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">userPreferAlipay</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">?</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">AlipayStrategy</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">WechatStrategy</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">strategy</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">pay</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">100</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">0</span><span class="p">);</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="模式选型速查">模式选型速查</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>场景</th>
          <th>推荐模式</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>需要全局唯一实例</td>
          <td>单例</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>对象创建逻辑复杂</td>
          <td>工厂/建造者</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>扩展功能不修改原类</td>
          <td>装饰器/代理</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>统一处理树形结构</td>
          <td>组合</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>运行时切换算法</td>
          <td>策略</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>解耦发送者和接收者</td>
          <td>观察者/命令</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>状态驱动不同行为</td>
          <td>状态</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>简化复杂系统调用</td>
          <td>外观</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<hr>
<h2 id="常见问题与误区">常见问题与误区</h2>
<h3 id="问题1为使用模式而使用模式">问题1：为使用模式而使用模式</h3>
<p><strong>根因</strong>：过度设计，简单问题复杂化
<strong>解决</strong>：KISS优先，模式是解决重复问题的工具，不是目标</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>